<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta name="robots" content="noindex">
<title>Message received — Strabo Insight</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=EB+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400;1,500&family=DM+Sans:opsz,wght@9..40,300;9..40,400;9..40,500;9..40,600&family=Space+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
:root {
  --navy: #091E38;
  --navy-deep: #060F1C;
  --gold: #C49A4A;
  --paper: #F7F4EE;
  --fh: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif;
  --fb: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
  --fm: 'Space Mono', monospace;
}
body {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  background: var(--navy-deep);
  color: var(--paper);
  font-family: var(--fb);
  text-align: center;
}
body::before {
  content: '';
  position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0; pointer-events: none;
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='1'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  opacity: 0.022;
}
main { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 32rem; }
.lbl {
  font-family: var(--fm);
  font-size: 0.58rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold);
  opacity: 0.7;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
h1 {
  font-family: var(--fh);
  font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3.25rem);
  font-weight: 500;
  line-height: 1.08;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }
p {
  font-size: 0.97rem;
  color: rgba(247,244,238,0.55);
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}
.btn-p {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--fb);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  background: var(--gold);
  color: var(--navy-deep);
  padding: 0.95rem 2.25rem;
  border-radius: 1px;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
}
.btn-p:hover { background: #d4aa5a; transform: translateY(-1px); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<main>
  <p class="lbl">Message received</p>
  <h1>We'll be in touch <em>soon.</em></h1>
  <p>Thanks for reaching out!</p>
  <a href="/" class="btn-p">Back to Strabo Insight</a>
</main>
</body>
</html>
